加入“可编辑属性道具”，玩家可自由编辑场景里道具的某些属性。此行为可打开编辑窗口: Add "Editable Property Item" to freely edit the properties of items in the scene. This behavior can open the edit window.
将物体放入背包。: Places an object in the Bag.
取消对象正目前所处的移动状态。注意，“移动状态”仅限通过行为“移动”实现的移动。: Cancels the movement status the object is in. Note that the "Movement Status" is limited to movement achieved through the behavior "Move."
取消对象正目前所处的跟随状态。注意，“跟随状态”仅限通过行为“跟随”实现的跟随。: Cancels the following status the object is in. Note that "Following Status" is limited to following achieved through the behavior "Follow."
判断条件成立后: After conditions are deemed to have been met
根据是否满足条件发送不同的事件，可以用来实现不同条件下执行不同的行为。: Different events are sent according to whether the conditions are met, which can be used to implement different behaviors under different conditions.
向整个场景里所有的对象广播一条事件，这一广播事件可以成为触发对象行为的触发条件。: Broadcasts an event to all objects in the scene. This broadcast event can trigger the objects' behaviors.
在对象上播放一个特效，可以指定特效的名称和时间等。: Plays an effect on the object. You can specify the name, time and other properties of the effect.
让物体以曲线的形式进行移动，通过设定高度、长度和路径点决定曲线形状。: Makes objects move along a curve. Determine the shape of the curve by setting the height, length and waypoints.
将对象位置变量或数值变量，插入到变量数组的队列头部或尾部中。: Inserts an object position variable or a numeric variable to the head or the rear of a variable array queue.
从变量数组的队列头部或尾部中获取到对象的位置变量或数值变量，并且存储到结果变量内: Fetches the position variable or numeric variable of an object from the head or the rear of the variable array queue, then stores it in the result variable.
设置对象进行平移。可设定移动方向、速度和距离等。移动可以与旋转状态并存。: Sets an object to pan. Allows you to set the direction, speed, distance, etc. of movement. Movement can coexist with rotation.
在移动中设置的方向，是以对象本身的前后左右朝向为标准: The direction of movement is based on the direction the object is facing.
取消对象按本身方向移动的状态。注意，仅限于通过行为“按本身方向移动”实现的移动: Cancels the object's movement in its original direction. Note that this is limited to movement achieved through the behavior "Move in Original Direction."
设置对象进行旋转。可以设定旋转速度、角度和距离等。旋转可以与移动、跟随状态并存。: Sets an object to rotate. Allows you to set the rotation speed, angle, distance, etc. Rotation can coexist with movement and following.
将对象设为激活/非激活状态。非激活状态下，对象在场景里不发生任何作用。: Activates or deactivates the object. When deactivated, the object has no impact on the scene.
给指定对象设定轴、最大距离和最小距离后，对象可以被手指拖动，超出距离范围则不可拖: After setting the axis, the maximum distance and the minimum distance for the specified object, the object can be dragged by a finger, but it cannot be dragged beyond the distance range.
将一个对象存到指定的对象存储器，当逻辑调用该对象存储器时，即可调出这个对象。: Saves an object to the specified object storage. When the logic calls the object storage, the object can be called out.
环境的重力值，决定角色的跳跃高度: Gravity of the environment. It determines characters' jump height.
设定场景的重力值，重力值决定角色下落时的速度。: Gravity of the scene. It determines characters' fall speed.
给场景中的变量、对象自定义属性等设置值，如修改某项游戏属性为一个具体数值。: Allows you to set values for variables and custom object properties in the scene, such as modifying a game property to a specific value.
更改隐藏/显示状态,更改激活状态,更改是否可碰撞,在对象上播放特效,移动,旋转,: Toggle between Hidden/Shown,Change Activation Status,Toggle Collision,Play Effect on Object,Move,Rotate,Follow,Cancel Movement,Cancel Rotation,Cancel Following,Set Gravity,Character's Speed Change
设置对象跟随另一个对象移动。可以设定跟随的时间。跟随可以与与旋转状态并存。: Sets an object to follow another object. Sets the duration of following. Following can coexist with rotation.
将对象移动到场景里另一个对象所在的位置。可以设定移动所需花费的时间。: Moves an object to another object in the scene. Sets the duration of movement.
将对象替换为另一个其他的道具、角色、物体或特效。: Replaces an object with another item, character, object, or effect.
将对象与场景中另一个对象连线，将随着该对象移动。: Connects two objects in the scene so one of them will follow the other.
解除对象与场景中另一个对象的连线关系。: Remove the connection of two objects in the scene.
在场景里新增一个道具、角色、物体或特效。可以设定新增对象的位置。: Adds an item, character, object, or effect to the scene. Sets the position of an added object.
新增一个与对象完全相同的道具、角色、物体或特效。: Adds to the scene an item, character, object, or effect identical to the object.
删除之后，对象将不再出现在场景中。与更改为“未激活”状态的对象不同在于，后者还能: Once deleted, the object will no longer appear in the scene. It's different from deactivated objects, which can be reactivated.
换成倒车档。动力不变。: Shifts into reverse. Keeps the momentum unchanged.
控制方向。单位是弧度。0是正前方。负的左转，正的右转，好像。: Controls the direction. The unit is radian. 0 is straight ahead. Negative = turn left; positive = turn right, I think.
设置手刹力度。手刹只影响前轮。: Sets the handbrake strength. The handbrake only affects the front wheels.
设置脚刹力度。越大刹车越快，太大可能引起震荡。: Sets the foot brake strength. The higher the value, the quicker the vehicle stops. A value too high could cause vibrations.
将角色更换皮肤。角色仅仅在外观上发生改变，属性不发生改变。: Changes character appearances. Changes character appearances and keeps the properties.
让对象的外形发生改变，但属性不发生改变，可在素材库内选择物体，作为变形后的外形。: Changes the object's appearance without changing its properties. You can select object in the material library as the new appearance.
无条件判定游戏失败。: Unconditionally determine that the game is lost.
朝向目标移动的最长用时如果达到时间还未到达目标点同样停止不继续向前移动: The maximum duration of an object's movement towards the target. If the object fails to reach the destination within the time frame, it stops.
距离目标多远停止: Distance from the Target before Stopping
停止后给指定对象发送事件: Send Events to Specified Objects after Stopping
此行为使角色可以朝着对象移动，仅限于角色，可以通过寻路避开障碍物前行。: This behavior allows characters to move towards objects and to avoid obstacles through pathfinding. For characters only.
